(1. Feedforward Neural Networks \(FNN\)) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 685.00 Tm
(Data moves only in one direction \(input -> output\).) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 669.00 Tm
(No memory of past inputs.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 653.00 Tm
(Used for basic classification/regression.) Tj
ET
BT
0.145 0.388 0.655 rg
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 631.00 Tm
(2. Vanishing Gradient Problem) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 614.00 Tm
(In deep networks, gradients become very small during backpropagation.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 598.00 Tm
(Earlier layers learn very slowly or stop learning.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 582.00 Tm
(Limits deep neural network training.) Tj
ET
BT
0.145 0.388 0.655 rg
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 560.00 Tm
(3. Convolutional Neural Networks \(CNNs\)) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 543.00 Tm
(Designed for image data.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 527.00 Tm
(Use filters to detect patterns like edges, shapes.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 511.00 Tm
(Widely used in computer vision.) Tj
ET
BT
0.145 0.388 0.655 rg
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 489.00 Tm
(4. Transformers) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 472.00 Tm
(Modern architecture for sequence data \(text\).) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 456.00 Tm
(Uses attention mechanism instead of recurrence.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 440.00 Tm
(Handles long-range dependencies better.) Tj
ET
BT
0.145 0.388 0.655 rg
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 418.00 Tm
(5. Self-Attention Mechanism) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 401.00 Tm
(Helps model understand which words are important.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 385.00 Tm
(Each word looks at other words in the sentence.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 369.00 Tm
(Captures context effectively.) Tj
ET
BT
0.145 0.388 0.655 rg
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 347.00 Tm
(6. Multi-Head Attention) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 330.00 Tm
(Multiple attention layers run in parallel.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 314.00 Tm
(Each learns different relationships.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 298.00 Tm
(Improves model understanding.) Tj
ET
BT
0.145 0.388 0.655 rg
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 276.00 Tm
