1 0 0 1 44.00 259.00 Tm
(Adds order information to input tokens.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 243.00 Tm
(Needed because transformers process data in parallel.) Tj
ET
BT
0.118 0.125 0.141 rg
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 44.00 227.00 Tm
(Without it -> model doesn't know sequence order.) Tj
